query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('acoustics',
'charge',
'coordinate-systems',
'energy-conservation',
'gauge-theory',
'group-theory',
'inertial-frames',
'quantum-electrodynamics',
'space-expansion',
'speed-of-light',
'time',
'universe');
